KillerOverride.Name: The Nurse
KillerOverride.KillerNotes:
A build may have either Annotated Blueprint OR Vigo's Blueprint, but never both.

Two Vigo's Shroud are required.

KillerOverride.Name: The Shape
KillerOverride.KillerNotes: The Shape has ZERO perk bans or restrictions (individual or combined). This overrides General Balancing (Ex: NOED + NWO can be used; PWYF, Hubris can be used; etc.)

KillerOverride.Name: The Twins
KillerOverride.KillerNotes: One survivor may pick Annotated Blueprint or Vigo's Blueprint, but not both.
